  "2026-07-06T09:26:35.474Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: implemented and verified relative LanceDB path anchoring through pmRoot-aware resolveVectorStores call sites in search, health, reindex, and semantic refresh. Focused linked test passed; temp-dir smoke from inside project/.agents/pm confirmed active LanceDB path anchored to project/.agents/pm/search/lancedb and no nested .agents/pm/.agents was created. Gates passed: pnpm build, pnpm lint, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pm health --check-only --summary --json ok, pm validate history_drift ok with pre-existing validate_resolution_missing_fields warning, full coverage 264 files / 5436 tests / 100% statements branches functions lines."
