  "2026-07-06T08:51:41.233Z",maintainer-agent,"Fix implemented and verified 2026-07-06 - anchorLanceDbStorePath in vector-stores.ts anchors relative paths to the workspace root (basename-based pm-root derivation, separator-safe); resolveVectorStores(settings, pmRoot?) optional param threaded through search.ts, health.ts (buildVectorizationRuntimeSnapshot), reindex.ts (assertSemanticRuntimeAvailable), cache.ts semantic-refresh context. cache.ts isSemanticRefreshActive left unanchored on purpose (boolean availability check only). 4 regression tests added to search-provider-store-selection.spec.ts (conventional root, bare root, absolute path, no-root back-compat); spec passes 20/20. Stray .agents/pm/.agents/ directory removed from the workspace. tsc clean."
