close_reason: Fixed relative LanceDB vector-store path anchoring and verified no nested workspace store is created
body: "Root cause: resolveLanceDbStore (src/core/search/vector-stores.ts) returned the raw settings path; consumers call resolve(storePath) which is cwd-dependent. pm-root discovery walks ancestors so item data stays correct, but the vector store forks.\n\nFix (working tree, session 2026-07-06): anchor relative lancedb paths to the workspace root derived from pmRoot (basename-based, separator-safe: <ws>/.agents/pm -> <ws>; bare --path roots anchor to themselves). resolveVectorStores(settings, pmRoot?) gained an optional backward-compatible param; call sites in search.ts, cache.ts (semantic refresh context) updated; health.ts buildVectorizationRuntimeSnapshot still needs pmRoot threading. Also remove the stray nested .agents/pm/.agents/ directory from the workspace.\n\nAcceptance: pm search/reindex/health run from a workspace subdirectory never create .agents/pm/.agents/**; unit test covers anchorLanceDbStorePath for conventional root, bare root, and absolute path."
